    Class Description
    CovidVerificationController
    The Controller class CovidVerificationController is marked as a REST controller with request mapping of "/covid".
    LoginController
    LoginController class is annotated for a RestController with RequestMapping at "/api/auth"

    Methods authenticateUser Authenticates the user. registerUser Registers a new user.
    PatientDiagnosisController
    Controller class PatientDiagnosisController maps to "/daignosis"

    Methods getActiveDiagnosis Get the active diagnosis getDiagnosisById Get a diagnosis by id getDiagnosisById Get all diagnosis addPatient Creates a new patient patientDiagnosisUpdate Changes information for a patient. removePatient delets a patient.

    allAccess guserAccess moderatorAccess adminAccess
    UserController
    Controller class UserController maps to /users

    Methods addUser Creates a new user in the DB getAllUsers Returns all the users getUser Gets a single user updateUser Changes information for a given user deleteUser Deletes a user for a given id
